{"tid":2220157,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CID涉偽造不追究口供被捕","createTime":"2020-09-27T12:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T15:45:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ffdbe261000c1afc77561261f6f3ac768a0a945b","tid":2220157,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:24:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/KHHY45BNEZEHLOZVYGLKBIJELQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2FKHHY45BNEZEHLOZVYGLKBIJELQ%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUk%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=ad208c3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2FKHHY45BNEZEHLOZVYGLKBIJELQ%2F&h=6ddb2f06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/KHHY45BNEZEHLOZVYGLKBIJELQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nCID涉偽造不追究口供被捕<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】再有警員知法犯法！今年4月，葵青警區刑事調查隊（CID）一名警員在青衣處理一宗店舖盜竊案時，涉嫌偽造不追究口供，其後被上級揭發，經調查後因涉嫌妨礙司法公正被捕，將停職受查。<br />\n<br />\n事發於4月13日，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u9HOYGkqyQKtAiwOONG5qijk0W0=/4896x3264/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YDIJ6KDGYNF4RDKZNQ5YTAOSGQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu9HOYGkqyQKtAiwOONG5qijk0W0%3D%2F4896x3264%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYDIJ6KDGYNF4RDKZNQ5YTAOSGQ.jpg&h=d789bc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新界南總區重案組接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冒簽遭揭發 保釋候查<br />\n<br />\n據了解，葵青警區刑事調查隊第六隊當日接報到場調查，處理該案件的22歲警員涉嫌偽造一份不追究口供，及偽造簽名，指報案人不再追究。上級其後發現不追究口供有可疑，因口供由員工代替機構負責人簽名，懷疑有人妨礙司法公正，於是致電報案人確認並揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n新界南總區重案組接手調查，並於前日（25日）在葵涌區拘捕涉事警員，。。。。。。。。。員干犯違法行為，定必嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，一般盜竊案件，即使拘捕疑犯，若證據不足、或調查後認為毋須送上法庭等，皆可以循不追究口供結案，惟需得到報案人同意。"},{"pid":"bfd4cb2f22fde1f01df548963d3fe4a5a91333d7","tid":2220157,"uid":95221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:27:23.000Z","msg":"佢上級咁唔妥佢？<br />\n<br />\n告得入先算"},{"pid":"c4adb1e4dc7f80d5dbdc79d2e12af537dd185049","tid":2220157,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"又唔係佢偷點解咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8d3330588053539425ebddd32a2e336c4b221d","tid":2220157,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:32:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">聽朝就會復職</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6bd83c2621e7485bfb9be1c19446da83f91a9bd","tid":2220157,"uid":266805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"睇嚟得罪人<br />\n比人篤"},{"pid":"9f3da253c88b0af88a3d8445cc0920c20b5256c7","tid":2220157,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:37:42.000Z","msg":"藍屍快去聲援呀蛇 <br />\n都係黑暴搞到呀蛇落假口供！"},{"pid":"cf071dfeda3fd1d1439fcbd29879f3c8e95dadb5","tid":2220157,"uid":276191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4adb1e4dc7f80d5dbdc79d2e12af537dd185049","tid":2220157,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"又唔係佢偷點解咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:39:34.000Z","msg":"可能犯案者係佢親友"},{"pid":"5bf93773a0bbfe7e8752178b0b634e099399929c","tid":2220157,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf071dfeda3fd1d1439fcbd29879f3c8e95dadb5","tid":2220157,"uid":276191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4adb1e4dc7f80d5dbdc79d2e12af537dd185049","tid":2220157,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"又唔係佢偷點解咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:39:34.000Z","msg":"可能犯案者係佢親友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:41:11.000Z","msg":"或者係純粹懶 唔想做野<img